title: Exercise: Use Temporary Uploads for End Users

questions.question: What would happen if you kept the XSD file selected after uploading it?
options: The workspace would fail because the XSD file is too big to upload.
The workspace would fail because it would run using the XSD as the GML input.
The workspace would fail because it cannot accept more than one input file.

questions.question: The Upload File button lets you upload multiple files at once.
